events.name: 移動（ノルヴァーナの街）

parameters: Kyle: Hey, good afternoon. You must be Luna.
Kyle: I'm Kyle, the leader of the Norvana Rebellion.
Kyle: I've heard rumors about you.

Kyle: The Blue Sorceress from the village of Sheena. And above all, a former
court magician and close aide to Lucia. It's an honor to meet you.

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] I'm sorry, Kyle-san. Luna feels very uncomfortable when people bring up her
past with Lucia.
Kyle: I see. My apologies for that.
Kyle: Hm? It looks like we have another guest.

Kyle: General Rinny of the Magi, huh? We have quite the distinguished guests
today.

Rinny: You are... Kyle, the former general of the Lyubel Kingdom. An unexpected
place to meet.

Kyle: Like the Knights of Messiah, I am one who has inherited the will of Lady
Reine.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Ah, the sound of a bell?
Kyle: It's the bell of prayer. It rings several times a day.

Kyle: The bell of prayer to commemorate those who died in the battle between the
royal army and the Valentia army. I had it made on my orders to the craftsmen.

Kyle: Here, we have many reliable professionals selected for combat. And you and
your friends are among them, Luna. We are comrades.

[Rima] My name is Rima. I'm a former lieutenant from the great nation of Glares.
We're comrades now. Nice to meet you.

[Rima] Outcast Rinny, we've had our differences in the past, but that's all in
the past now.

Rinny: Hmph... Outcast Rinny, huh? That's a derogatory nickname for me, but
alright. Nice to meet you.

[Rima] My apologies. I heard you've mellowed out since joining the Knights of
Messiah. Heh heh.

[Wendy] I'm Wendy, Rima's younger sister. I'm not a warrior but a caretaker and
jack-of-all-trades. Nice to meet you. Ehehe!
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Nice to meet you. Rima, Wendy, Jack.
Kyle: Hey now, you guys aren't involved in this.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Hehe, nice to meet you. Lilim, Polo.
Lilim: Everyone here is an incredibly strong hero~!
Polo: We're all heroes, you know~!

\C[24][Cain]\C[0] Now that you mention it, there were some dirty brats like you guys in the
village of Misa~.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Mei and Mao, right? I wonder how they're doing now.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Kyle-san, I've really taken a liking to this place.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] May I start working on something right away?
Kyle: Then, may I entrust you with an important mission?

Kyle: No, Luna is an exceptional mage. Even Lucia and Sylvia hold her in high
regard. If this job goes well, it could be a breakthrough.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Understood. Please let me take on that important mission.
Kyle: Alright. Talk to me once you're ready.
Kyle: The place I want you to head to is the "Ruins of Levius."
Kyle: Yes, the "Key to the Holy Grail" is there.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The Key to the Holy Grail?
Kyle: It's the key to obtain "Regnus Grahardt's Holy Grail."

Kyle: There's a place where the Holy Grail is located, but without the key, you
can't enter. I want you to retrieve that key.

Kyle: If the legend is true, the Holy Grail can bring out the maximum potential
of whoever touches it.

Kyle: If we can maximize our abilities with the power of the Holy Grail, we
might be able to defeat them.

Kyle: After obtaining the Holy Grail, we will take down Lucia and the generals
of Valentina ourselves.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Understood. I will definitely secure the Key to the Holy Grail.

Kyle: This is the 'Ruins of Levius.' I've heard it's full of thieves and brutes
looking for treasure. Be careful.
Luna and her companions headed towards the 'Ruins of Levius.'

Kyle: Truthfully, we would like to accompany you, but there's a chance this
place could be attacked while we're away. We're counting on you.

Kyle: What a disaster... I never imagined it would come to this... Luna, it
seems futile to stop you. We who couldn't protect Mei and Mao have no right to
stop you...
Jack: "Luna, I sincerely welcome you as a member of our group."
Jack: "What a thing to happen... Luna, I'm sorry."
Rima: "It's a place with nothing much, but please make yourself comfortable."

Rima: Luna... I'm the one to blame. Wendy has no combat abilities. At that time,
I was the only one who could fight. But... when faced with them, I couldn't do
anything... Mei and Mao were protecting you until the very end... I can't find
the words to apologize to you.

Rima: "My sister Rima used to be a general of Glares, that now non- existent
mighty nation. As for me, her little sister, I can't do much though~ Teehee."
Rima: Luna, I'm sorry... Mei... Mao... Why... Why did it come to this...

Lilim: "Everyone here is a hero among heroes~. They were chosen in the previous
battle, after all."
\C[20][Noah]\C[0] "I'm gonna be just like everyone here when I grow up~."
